  "texts": [
    "Even if it just helps me like kill roaches in my house.",
    "(P07) 4.2.1.2 Extrinsic motivations: Professional and social.",
    "Some of our participants were employed in a professional red team at a company, and some were researchers in security, safety and natural language processing.",
    "Obviously, these participants had a professional motivation or \"monetary incentives\" (P21).",
    "A professional motivation may also include a desire to \"stay on top of things\" and improve one's own hireability: \"my external motivation, if I want to have a chance of keep working in natural language processing, I better start understanding what is going on here quick\" (P02)\"it's a banal answer."
